high_descs: Turn to the right and then find the large dresser across the room.
Pick up the orange colored pencil from the back of the dresser.
Hold the pencil and look down.
Open the top drawer and place the pencil inside.
Take out a cup with the pencil inside. Shut the drawer.
Carry the cup and turn around. Walk back to the small brown dresser with a lamp.
Place the cup on the dresser, to the right side.
anns.task_desc: Move a pencil to a cup and move them both to a dresser.

high_descs: Turn around, hang a left at the bed and walk to the black dresser ahead.
Pick up the yellow pen on the dresser in the middle.
Look down at the cabinets below the top of the dresser.
Open the middle lower cabinet and put the pen inside the black mug.
Pick up the mug with the pen inside and close the door.
Turn around, turn right, hang a left at the door and walk to the small nightstand next to the bed.
Put the mug with the pen on the front right corner of the nightstand.
anns.task_desc: Place a mug with a pen on a nightstand.

high_descs: Turn left, move to the cabinet, right of the computer.
Pick up the pen from the counter top.
Move to the counter, left side, in front of the right hand door.
Put the pen in the cup below the cabinet.
Pick up the cup from below the cabinet.
Turn right, move to the nightstand near the door.
Put the cup on the nightstand.
anns.task_desc: Place a cup containing a pen onto the nightstand.
